    dc:description "FIGURES 8 – 11. Isosecuriflustra pinniformis n. sp., type specimens, off São Paulo, Brazil. 8, MZUSP 0 277 (holotype specimen) in left (A) and MZUSP 0 278 (paratype specimen) in right (B); 9, close-up of basal rhizoids of paratype colony; 10 – 11, MZUSP 0 277, holotype specimen; 10, distal end of colony; 11, close-up of ovicelled zooids." ;
